'''卑詩新民主黨'''（{{lang-en|New Democratic Party of British Columbia}}，簡稱BC NDP）是[[加拿大|加拿大]][[卑詩省|卑詩省]]的主要政黨之一，現時為該省的[[執政黨|執政黨]]。該黨以[[左翼|左翼]]政黨的姿態參政<ref name="WarrenKarena2003">{{cite book|author1=Magnusson, Warren|author2=Shaw, Karena|title=A Political Space: Reading the Global Through Clayoquot Sound|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=I2_bd0lR97YC&pg=PA18|accessdate=2013-05-04|year=2003|publisher=U of Minnesota Press|isbn=978-0-8166-4039-3|pages=18–}}</ref>，政治理念為[[社會民主主義|社會民主主義]]。該黨為[[加拿大新民主黨|加拿大新民主黨]]的省級分支，黨員同時隸屬省級和聯邦層面的新民主黨。該黨的現任黨魁為[[賀謹|賀謹]]。

==歷史==
該黨於1933年成立，當時為合作社聯邦聯合會（{{lang|en|Co-operative Commonwealth Federation}}，簡稱CCF）的卑詩省分支，由加拿大社會黨卑詩分部、社會重建聯盟（{{lang|en|League for Social Reconstruction}}）及其它附屬機構組成。該黨於1933年省選中贏取7個議席，成為官方反對黨<ref name="Hist">{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/canada/bcvotes2009/story/2009/03/24/bcv-new-democratic-party-profile.html|title=B.C. New Democratic Party profile|author=Mike Laanela|publisher=CBC News|accessdate=2013-05-05|date=2009-04-06|archive-date=2013-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130524093152/http://www.cbc.ca/canada/bcvotes2009/story/2009/03/24/bcv-new-democratic-party-profile.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。CCF於1960年更名為新黨（{{lang|en|New Party}}），再於翌年改稱新民主黨<ref name="Hist"/>。在黨魁巴勒特（{{lang|en|Dave Barrett}}）的領導下，卑詩新民主黨於1972年省選中贏取38席，並壓倒社信黨首度上台執政。然而，新民主黨於1975年省選中敗於社信黨，恢復在野黨地位<ref name="Hist"/>。

1991年，執政社信黨黨魁[[溫德心|溫德心]]因捲入利益衝突醜聞而宣佈下台，並拖累社信黨民望。新民主黨在黨魁哈葛（{{lang|en|Mike Harcourt}}）領導下於同年省選贏取51席，重奪執政地位<ref name="Hist"/>。然而，新民主黨於1990年代中期亦陷入所謂“泵波拿事件”（{{lang|en|Bingo-gate}}）的政治醜聞；哈葛本人雖然沒有置身其中，但仍宣佈下台以示政治問責<ref name="星島110226">{{cite web |url=http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2011-02-26/headline1298719896d3029570.html |title=遭醜聞拖累　近代省長多黯然下台 |publisher=《星島日報》加西版 |date=2011-02-26 |accessdate=2013-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160407145054/http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2011-02-26/headline1298719896d3029570.html |archive-date=2016-04-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。新民主黨在民調中本來落後[[卑詩自由黨|卑詩自由黨]]，但新任黨魁[[簡嘉年|簡嘉年]]卻於1996年省選中帶領新民主黨壓倒自由黨，保住執政黨地位<ref name="Hist"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.elections.bc.ca/docs/rpt/1996-SOVGeneralElection.pdf |title=Statements of Votes: 36th Provincial General Election |publisher=Elections BC |date=1997-02-10 |accessdate=2013-04-16 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923235204/http://www.elections.bc.ca/docs/rpt/1996-SOVGeneralElection.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

簡嘉年本人於1999年捲入醜聞而下台<ref name="CBC990821c">{{cite news|title=Glen Clark steps down under pressure|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/story/1999/08/21/clarkii990821.html|accessdate=2013-04-24|publisher=CBC News|date=1999-08-21}}</ref>；[[苗禮義|苗禮義]]擔任臨時黨魁，至[[杜新志|杜新志]]於2000年2月當選黨魁為止。在多項不利因素影響下，新民主黨於2001年省選中大敗予自由黨，在省議會的79席中只保住兩席，為歷屆省議會中最懸殊的議會分佈<ref name="Hist"/>。選後杜新志辭任黨魁，並由省議會内僅餘兩名新民主黨黨籍議員之一麥菲（{{lang|en|Joy McPhail}}）擔任臨時黨魁。

[[詹嘉路|詹嘉路]]在2003年當選黨魁，並於2005年省選中帶領新民主黨贏取33個議席，整體得票率更超越40%，為1991年以來的首次。2009年省選，新民主黨贏取35個議席，整體得票率為42%，稍遜自由黨的45%<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.elections.bc.ca/docs/rpt/2009-GE-Ref-Report.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-11-08 |archive-date=2011-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111230232323/http://www.elections.bc.ca/docs/rpt/2009-GE-Ref-Report.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年12月，資深黨員[[關慧貞|關慧貞]]公開批評詹嘉路的領導方式，並要求立刻舉行黨領選舉<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://thetyee.ca/News/2010/12/02/KwansAttack/ |title=James Allies Scramble to Defend Against Kwan's Attack |publisher=''The Tyee'' |date=2010-12-02 |first=Andrew |last=MacLeod |accessdate=2014-11-08 |archive-date=2014-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108165327/http://thetyee.ca/News/2010/12/02/KwansAttack/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://thetyee.ca/Blogs/TheHook/Election-Central/2010/12/01/KwanJames/ |title='Carole James is dividing the party': NDP MLA Kwan |publisher=''The Tyee'' |date=2010-12-01 |first=Andrew |last=MacLeod |accessdate=2014-11-08 |archive-date=2014-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108165653/http://thetyee.ca/Blogs/TheHook/Election-Central/2010/12/01/KwanJames/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.vancouversun.com/news/leader+Carole+James+will+convene+emergency+meeting+over+revolt/3918385/story.html |title=NDP leader Carole James will convene emergency meeting over revolt |publisher=''[[溫哥華太陽報|Vancouver Sun]]'' |date=2010-12-02 |first=Jonathan |last=Fowlie |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110307055621/http://www.vancouversun.com/news/leader+Carole+James+will+convene+emergency+meeting+over+revolt/3918385/story.html |archivedate=2011-03-07 |accessdate=2014-11-08 }}</ref>；詹嘉路於同月請辭，由白瞳恩（{{lang|en|Dawn Black}}）出任臨時黨魁<ref name="James resigns Sun">{{Cite news |url=http://www.vancouversun.com/news/Carole+James+quits+leader/3934785/story.html |title=Carole James quits as NDP leader |publisher=''[[溫哥華太陽報|Vancouver Sun]]'' |date=2010-12-06 |first=Jonathan and Rob Shaw |last=Fowlie |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110316060029/http://www.vancouversun.com/news/Carole+James+quits+leader/3934785/story.html |archivedate=2011-03-16 |accessdate=2014-11-08 }}</ref><ref name='James resigns Globe'>{{Cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/british-columbia/carole-james-standing-down/article1826894/ |title=Carole James Standing Down |publisher=[[環球郵報|Globe and Mail]] |date=2010-12-06 |first=Justine |last=Hunter |accessdate=2014-11-08 |archive-date=2010-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101209140057/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/british-columbia/carole-james-standing-down/article1826894/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，至[[狄德安|狄德安]]於2011年4月當選黨魁為止<ref name="星島130320">{{cite web |author=張文慈 |url=http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2013-03-20/headline1363774821d4408583.html |title=父母薰陶 怕醜草投身政治 |publisher=《星島日報》加西版 |date=2013-03-20 |accessdate=2013-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105050152/http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2013-03-20/headline1363774821d4408583.html |archive-date=2013-11-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2013年省選前夕，新民主黨本來形勢大好，在選前民調中一度以20個百分點領先自由黨。然而，新民主黨在大選中卻未能壓倒自由黨，更較選前失掉兩個議席。狄德安於同年9月辭任黨魁<ref name=resign>{{cite news|title=Adrian Dix resigns as B.C. NDP Leader|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/british-columbia/adrian-dix-expected-to-clarify-political-future-in-afternoon-announcement/article14396110/|accessdate=2013-09-18|newspaper=Globe and Mail|date=2013-09-18|archive-date=2015-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108161237/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/british-columbia/adrian-dix-expected-to-clarify-political-future-in-afternoon-announcement/article14396110/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而[[賀謹|賀謹]]則於2014年在無對手競爭的情況下自動當選黨魁<ref name="星島140501">{{cite web |url=http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2014-05-01/province1398937318d5030795.html |title=NDP唯一黨領候選人 賀謹當選料無懸念 |publisher=《星島日報》加西版 |date=2014-05-01 |accessdate=2014-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108165540/http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2014-05-01/province1398937318d5030795.html |archive-date=2014-11-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2017年省選，新民主黨和自由黨分別贏取41席和43席，兩者皆不能以多數政府姿態執政，持有3席的卑詩綠黨遂成為執政之鍵。賀謹領導下的新民主黨於同年5月29日與卑詩綠黨達成協議，讓新民主黨在綠黨的支持下於該屆省議會以少數政府姿態執政<ref name="CBC170529">{{cite news|title=B.C. Green Party agrees to support NDP in the legislature|url=http://www.cbc.ca/beta/news/canada/british-columbia/bc-ndp-green-agreement-1.4136539|accessdate=2017-06-30|publisher=CBC News|date=2017-05-29|first=Justin|last=McElroy|archive-date=2017-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170603134056/http://www.cbc.ca/beta/news/canada/british-columbia/bc-ndp-green-agreement-1.4136539|dead-url=no}}</ref>。賀謹於同年6月29日在省議會向自由黨政府提出[[不信任動議|不信任動議]]，以44-42票通過，自由黨遂失去執政地位<ref name="CBC170629a">{{cite news|title=B.C. Liberal government loses confidence vote 44-42, sparking either NDP government or election|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/bc-liberals-fall-non-confidence-1.4185005|accessdate=2017-06-30|publisher=CBC News|date=2017-06-29|first=Justin|last=McElroy|archive-date=2017-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171104160802/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/bc-liberals-fall-non-confidence-1.4185005|dead-url=no}}</ref>。卑詩省省督古桑（{{lang|en|Judith Guichon}}）隨後邀請賀謹籌組政府，新民主黨遂重拾執政權<ref name="CBC170629b">{{cite news|title=NDP Leader John Horgan to be next premier of British Columbia|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/horgan-government-guichon-2017-1.4185204|accessdate=2017-06-30|publisher=CBC News|date=2017-06-29|first=Justin|last=McElroy|archive-date=2017-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170630112221/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/horgan-government-guichon-2017-1.4185204|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

